55 }

57 }

62 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_MEMORY);
63 return (0);
64 }
65
66 np->np_nt = nt;

68 if ((np->np_name = strdup(var_name)) == NULL) {

71 return (0);
72 }
73
74 STAILQ_INSERT_TAIL(&nt->nt_nplist, np, np_next);
75
76 return (1);
77}
